CustomField.formula: IF(OR(ISBLANK(E2__c), E2__c = 0), "", "E2: " + TEXT(E2__c) + " ") & IF(OR(ISBLANK(LH__c), LH__c = 0), "", "LH: " + TEXT(LH__c) + " ") & IF(OR(ISBLANK(P4__c), P4__c = 0), "", "P4: " + TEXT(P4__c) + " ") & IF(ISBLANK(HCG__c), "", IF(HCG__c = 0, "HCG: <5 ", "HCG: " + TEXT(HCG__c) + " ")) & IF(ISBLANK(Left_Follicle_Summary__c), "", "Left Folls: " + Left_Follicle_Summary__c + " ") & IF(ISBLANK(Right_Follicle_Summary__c), "", "Right Fols: " + Right_Follicle_Summary__c + " ") & IF(OR(ISBLANK(Endometrium_Thickness__c), Endometrium_Thickness__c = 0), "", "ET: " + TEXT(Endometrium_Thickness__c) + " ") & IF(ISBLANK(TEXT(Endometrium_Type__c)), "", "Endometrium Type: " + TEXT(Endometrium_Type__c))
CustomField.label: Doctor Result Summary
